    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.36.20"/>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">20</fw>
                
                <opener>
                    <dateline>February 13, 1972</dateline>
                
                    <salute>Dear Dr. Neihardt:</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>I cannot find the right words to thank you, Dr. Neihardt, for the very beautiful and moving dedication you have written. All I can tell you is this, when I finished reading the last lines the tears were streaming down my face.</p>
                
                <p>Your last four sentences are surely something that will be quoted frequently after you and I are both long gone from this scene of our endeavors.</p>
                
                <p>And when I think how much time it must have t<del>k</del><add>a</add>ken from you, <del>r</del> who still have so much to do on your autobiography, I feel guilty at being selfish enough to ask you to do this for me and the Sod House Society.</p>
                
                <p>'Surely, nothing on the outside wanted in; and nothing on the inside wanted out. But it seemed like closing the door upon a silent room where someone dear is sleeping and greatly needs the rest'. You see, I am doing this work for my father and mother who have been so long gone, yet are so alive in my memory.</p> 
                
                <p>You shall have a proof to check.</p> 
                
                <p>A mere thank you is not enough, perhaps at some future time I can do soemthing for you.</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>Cordially yours,</salute>
                    
                    <signed>Frances Alberts</signed>
                    <signed>Frances Alberts</signed>
                    <add>
                        <address>
                            <addrLine>1119 North Elm</addrLine> 
                            <addrLine>Hastings, Neb 68901</addrLine> 
                        </address>
                    </add>
                </closer>
                
            </div1>
